snippet.title: Tales of Symphonia Chronicles TGS 2013 Trailer
snippet.description:
Tales of Symphonia, and its sequel Dawn of the New World, are back in an HD pack with the choice of Japanese or English voice overs for the first time in Tales history!

The Collector's Edition is available for Pre-order, but supply is limited! 

Tales of Symphonia Chronicles is out early 2014 on Playstation 3. The long awaited return to Sylvarant and Tethe'alla !
For more information, please visit your local Namco Bandai Games website, http://www.namcobandaigames.com
Check out the official Facebook page too! http://www.facebook.com/tales
